name: Tree of Life (hard)
description:
To add insult to injury, the zombies have taken all but two drawings from
Heidi! Please help her recover the Tree of Life from only these two drawings.
Input The input format is the same as in the medium version, except that now
the bound on n is 2 ≤ n ≤ 1000 and that k = 2. Output The same as in the
medium version. Example Input 1 9 2 6 4 3 5 4 6 1 8 6 8 2 7 1 5 8 6 8 7 8 1 7
3 5 1 Output YES 2 1 3 1 5 4 6 5 7 6 8 5 9 8 1 4
